          <p class="text-sm mb-3">Full-res photos from camera are 20-50MB each. Uncompressed galleries load painfully slow. Compress to 300KB-1MB per image for web display. Keep original files for client delivery, display compressed versions on website. Tools: TinyPNG, ImageOptim, Squoosh. 90% file size reduction with minimal quality loss. Google penalizes slow sites in rankings—fast loading equals better SEO. Visitors abandon sites taking 3+ seconds to load.</p>
