          <h3 class="text-2xl font-black mb-3">LAZY LOADING</h3>
          <p class="text-sm mb-3">Only load images when viewer scrolls to them. 50-image gallery loads first 10 immediately, rest load as needed. Reduces initial page load by 80%. Most builders (Squarespace, Framer, Webflow) enable lazy loading by default. Verify it's enabled—check page speed insights. Lazy loading transforms 50-photo gallery from 15-second load to 3-second load. User experience matters: fast galleries feel professional, slow galleries feel amateur.</p>
          <div class="text-xs font-black bg-white/20 p-2">FEATURE: Enabled by default on quality builders</div>
